<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/611361-i-m-hoping-that-someone-can-help-me-i">I&#39;m hoping that someone can help me. I don&#39;t have a copy of the book in front of me and I am trying to remember the name of the soldier who took control when the prisoners were herded on to a ship. Plus maybe a few details of the incident? As the story is told, he stepped forward and took charge in a way that seemed completely counter to his personality before that time.
If anyone can help me, I&#39;d appreciate it.</a>
</div>
