<span id="freeTextContainer3188427741666017874">Took me along time to read as I got bogged down with the POWs life in the camp, all that background. I wanted to read the book for the raid itself, not for life from 1942 to 1945, So that part went very slow, But the fall of Bataan and the raid itself I really enjoyed, The planning was brilliant - to carry off a raid with very few casualties was unique. Good history.</span>

